author: @sgt.pepper1956
content: Copacabana is pretty much the only place where it is even possible to have 1,5million people for a concert. It is a very long and wide beach. Plus it is the pace where everybody goes in RIO. Stones did this in 2006. same amount of people. Both artist are truly world wide super stars.
